Henri Étiévant https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Henri_%C3%89ti%C3%A9vant 0 Henri Étiévant (13 March 1870 – 9 August 1953) was a French actor. Born Henri Gaston Étiévan-Estival in Paris, he died in 1953 in the 11th arrondissement of Paris. Henri_Étiévant ( 13_March_1870 – 9_August_1953 ) was a_French_actor .
